Design Philosophy

‚ú® Modern ‚Äî Clean lines, generous whitespace, contemporary aesthetics

üéØ Premium ‚Äî High-end feel comparable to Vercel, Linear, Stripe

üè¢ Enterprise-Ready ‚Äî Professional, trustworthy, scalable appearance

‚ö° Performance-First ‚Äî Sub-3s load times, optimized Core Web Vitals

Backend Architecture

Component	Technology	Purpose

Language	Go (Golang)	High performance, concurrency
API Design	RESTful + GraphQL	Flexible, efficient data fetching
Database	PostgreSQL	Reliable, ACID-compliant storage
Caching Layer	Redis	Session management, rate limiting
Authentication	JWT + OAuth 2.0	Secure, stateless auth
Queue System	RabbitMQ / NATS	Async task processing

Infrastructure Layer

Component	Technology	Function

Virtualization	Proxmox VE (KVM)	VPS provisioning & management
Containerization	Docker + Docker Compose	App hosting isolation
Orchestration	Kubernetes (optional)	Scalable container management
Core Ecosystem	Nextcloud	File management, collaboration
Reverse Proxy	Traefik / Nginx	Traffic routing, SSL termination


