- E-Wallets (GoPay, OVO, DANA)
- Convenience Store (Alfamart, Indomaret)

Automation:

Webhook listener for payment confirmation

Auto-activate service on successful payment

Auto-suspend after 3-day grace period

Auto-terminate after 14-day suspension

Invoice generation (PDF)

Receipt emails


Notification System

Email (Self-Hosted SMTP):
Provider: Custom SMTP Server
Configuration:
- SPF Record: Required ‚úì
- DKIM Signing: Required ‚úì
- DMARC Policy: Required ‚úì

