Layer	Implementation

Transport	HTTPS everywhere (Cloudflare SSL)
Application	OWASP Top 10 compliance
Authentication	bcrypt password hashing, JWT rotation
Authorization	Role-Based Access Control (RBAC)
Rate Limiting	Redis-based, per-IP and per-user
Input Validation	Server-side sanitization, prepared statements
Webhook Security	HMAC signature verification
Audit Logging	Immutable event logs, tamper detection
Backup Strategy	Daily automated backups, 30-day retention
DDoS Protection	Cloudflare proxy, rate limiting


