---

üìù Notes for Development

> Design Priority: The UI must feel premium from the first interaction. Study Vercel, Linear, and Stripe for inspiration. Every animation, every transition, every micro-interaction matters.



> Performance First: Lazy load everything possible. Optimize images. Use edge caching. The platform should feel instant.



> Security Always: Never trust user input. Validate everything server-side. Log security events. Regular penetration testing.



> Documentation: Every API endpoint documented. Every feature has a help article. Good docs reduce support load.




